## Representatives

Representatives act on behalf of <%= @current_collective.name %> through sessions during which their actions are recorded and made visible here.

<% if @current_collective.any_member_can_represent? %>
<%= @current_collective.name %> is configured to allow any member to represent the studio.
<% else %>
<%= @current_collective.name %> currently has <%= @representatives.count %> representative<%= @representatives.count == 1 ? '' : 's' %>.

<% @representatives.each do |representative| %>
* [<%= representative.display_name %>](<%= representative.path %>) (representative)
<% end %>
<% end %>

